# Walkthrough — WinNative UI Overhaul

## Changes Made

### 1. UnifiedActivity Redesign
[UnifiedActivity.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/UnifiedActivity.kt) — Complete rewrite:

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **PS5 carousel** | Horizontal `LazyRow`, center item scales to 1.12x with accent glow shadow |
| **Adaptive tabs** | AIO: Library/Downloads/Store · Non-AIO: Library/Downloads/Steam/Epic/GOG/Amazon |
| **Centered shadow pill** | `wrapContentWidth()` so pill adapts to visible tab count |
| **Steam status picker** | Circular avatar → dropdown with Online/Away/Invisible |
| **Circle shadows** | On Settings, Controller, and Profile buttons |
| **Filter panel** | Bottom-left icon opens slide-up panel (AIO toggle, store toggles, content type filters) |

